WHAT PROBLEM IT SOLVES
Replaces RED’s proprietary SDK-dependent Log3G10 inverse with an open,
verified mathematical transform. Ensures that V-RAPTOR footage linearized
via GIOP matches the original scene light to within 10⁻⁶ relative error,
enabling accurate compositing and cross‑camera matching.

